The F-Spot is a responsive and user-friendly website designed to provide an exceptional online shopping experience. It features a variety of functionalities, including product listings, a registration form, a favorites section, and a cart with checkout capabilities. The website is built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, ensuring compatibility across multiple devices and browsers.

Features
Home Page: Introduction to the website with a slider showcasing featured products.
Product Listings: Display of products with options to add to favorites and cart.
Favorites: A section to view and manage favorite products.
Cart: A detailed view of products added to the cart with a checkout form.
Registration Form: User registration with validation.
Responsive Design: Ensures compatibility across various devices and screen sizes.
Project Structure
bash
Copy code
